{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a6bee53097","title":"反对南非联邦政府的“种族隔离法案","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f3fca39b32","index":0,"year":1950,"month":7,"day":26,"articleId":"a6bee53097"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/29-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji29":{"comments":[{"id":"8e9a049729","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"a6bee53097","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东给达杜的电报。“种族隔离法案”，南非议会1950年5月通过的《集团住区法》。这是南非联邦政府歧视和压迪有色人种的法案。它把占南非联邦人口2/3以上的非白种人（指非洲土著人、印度人和少数中国人等）禁在几个隔离地区以内。"}],"contents":[{"id":"1ff94b6433","type":"title","text":"反对南非联邦政府的“种族隔离法案”叫","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"a6bee53097"},{"id":"8e9a049729","type":"paragraph","text":"南非达兰士瓦州印度人大会主席约瑟夫·达杜博士","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"a6bee53097"},{"id":"7d7a397597","type":"paragraph","text":"六月十八日来电收到。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"a6bee53097"},{"id":"04eff7bfe3","type":"paragraph","text":"我代表中国人民完全支持你们对于南非联邦政府歧视中、印及其他亚洲人民的所谓“种族隔离法案”的合理的抗议","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"a6bee53097"},{"id":"49608b973e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"a6bee53097"},{"id":"6a50c7c418","type":"paragraph","text":"北京七月二十六日","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"a6bee53097"}],"page":{"id":"8f87d27918","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"a6bee53097","start":48,"end":48}}}},"__N_SSG":true}